# Web Scraping Project - CodeAlpha Internship

## Project Overview
This project uses Python and BeautifulSoup to scrape book data from a public website.

## Technologies Used
- Python
- BeautifulSoup
- Requests
- Pandas

## Features
- Extracts book titles and prices
- Stores data in CSV format
- Demonstrates HTML parsing and web scraping

## Files Included
- scraper.py
- scraped_books.csv
- report.docx
- requirements.txt

## How to Run

### Install Libraries
pip install -r requirements.txt

### Run Project
python scraper.py
